OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773861072
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to much loved man
OL,4,Ctragically found dead in Coventry
OL,6,FThe family of a man whose body was
OL,7,Ffound in Coventry say they will always
OL,8,Fremember him as a "pillar of strength".
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police says
OL,11,Finvestigations are continuing after
OL,12,Fthe discovery of a body in a wheelie
OL,13,Fbin in a park off Daimler Road.
OL,15,FThey have now confirmed the body to be
OL,16,Fthat of Thomas Niven.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773861072
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to much loved man
OL,4,Ctragically found dead in Coventry
OL,6,FThe family of Mr Niven say the 37-year-
OL,7,Fold had a "vibe for life" and are
OL,8,Furging anyone with information about
OL,9,Fwhat happened to him to contact the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FA statement released by the family
OL,13,Fthrough the police, reads: "Sadly our
OL,14,Fyoungest son, stepson, brother,
OL,15,Fbrother in law, nephew and uncle, Tom
OL,16,Fhas been tragically taken away from
OL,17,Fall who dearly loved him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773861072
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to much loved man
OL,4,Ctragically found dead in Coventry
OL,6,F"As a family we are all in shock and
OL,7,Fare devastated, our hearts are in
OL,8,Fpieces at the loss of Tom in such a
OL,9,Fcruel way. He was a pillar of strength
OL,10,Ftowards us all.
OL,12,F"He was loving and caring, he loved
OL,13,Fall of his family, he was a big softy
OL,14,Fwhen it came to animals and his
OL,15,Fnephews and nieces.
OL,17,F"He was full of laughter and had such
OL,18,Fa vibe for life, he had a charm that
OL,19,Fwould lift a dull spirit, he loved his
OL,20,Fmusic and playing pool.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773861072
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to much loved man
OL,4,Ctragically found dead in Coventry
OL,6,F"He loved small harmless pranks, but
OL,7,Fcould never keep a straight face and
OL,8,Fwould break out into a laughter.
OL,10,F"We are so proud to have had Tom in
OL,11,Four lives, his life has tragically
OL,12,Fbeen cut short in the most cruel way.
OL,13,FTom will forever be missed.
OL,15,F"We love you Tom, rest easy, love us
OL,16,Fall Dad, Mum, stepmom, brothers and
OL,17,Fsisters, nephews and nieces and
OL,18,Fextended family.
OL,20,F"We urge anyone with information to
OL,21,Fplease come forward to the police."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773861072
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to much loved man
OL,4,Ctragically found dead in Coventry
OL,6,FA man and woman in their 40s and a man
OL,7,Fin his 20s were arrested on Sunday in
OL,8,FBlackpool on suspicion of murder and
OL,9,Fassisting an offender.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Phil Poole,
OL,12,Ffrom West Midlands Police's major
OL,13,Fcrime unit, said: "We are continuing
OL,14,Fto build a picture of what happened
OL,15,Fand the three people arrested at the
OL,16,Fweekend remain in police cells as
OL,17,Fthose enquiries continue.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773861072
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to much loved man
OL,4,Ctragically found dead in Coventry
OL,6,F"We'd like to thank everyone who has
OL,7,Fbeen in touch providing information so
OL,8,Ffar and we would still urge anyone who
OL,9,Fmight know more to still get in
OL,10,Fcontact."
OL,12,FAnyone with information can call 101,
OL,13,Fquoting log 4148 of 13 March, or
OL,14,Fmessage the police via their Live Chat
OL,15,Fon their website.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
